cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.CE 

This paper deals with the problem of Influence Maximization and Cost-aware Target Viral Marketing in online social networks, which are topics related to social networks and data science. Therefore, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SOC (Social and Cultural Anthropology) are the most likely categories. Additionally, the paper proposes an algorithm that uses Integer Programming, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Finally, the scalability of the algorithm is emphasized, which relates to cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
